Nutrient data for: CADBURY DAIRY MILK CHOCOLATE RASPBERRY, UNPREPARED, GTIN: 07622210497352
Food Group:  Branded Food Products Database

Ingredients: MILK**, sugar, vegetable fats (palm, shea), cocoa butter, skimmed MILK powder, cocoa mass, reduced fat cocoa powder (2%), whey powder (from MILK), chopped HAZELNUTS (1.4%), freeze-dried raspberry pieces (1%), emulsifiers (SOYA lecithin, E442, E476, sunflower lecithin), flavourings. **The equivalent of 426ml of fresh liquid milk in every 227g of milk chocolate.MILK CHOCOLATE: MILK SOLIDS 20% MINIMUM, ACTUAL 23%.CONTAINS VEGETABLE FATS IN ADDITION TO COCOA BUTTER. MAY CONTAIN OTHER NUTS, WHEAT. Date available: 11/10/2017 Date last updated by company: 09/08/2017
